==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: dateless
<hw>date"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Without date; having
no fixed time.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>not having a social companion for an occasion;
<as>as, to be <ex>dateless</ex> for the prom</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Date line</ent>⟦br⟧
